title: Hawaii volcano eruption enters new phase as crater falls quiet
content: (Reuters) - As lava continued to pour vigorously from the ground through fissures at the foot of Kilauea Volcano, the month-old eruption on Hawaii's Big Island has entered a new, seemingly calmer phase inside the summit crater, government scientists said on Friday....
